data.description: Lovely townhouse in sough-after Village of Owen Brown community located  just minutes from Columbia Mall , HWY 29 and HWY 32. Features new roof, new carpet in the bedrooms, hardwood floors on main level, three full bathrooms (one full bath in the basement), granite counter top, assigned parking space and much more. Seller requests Worldwide Settlement as title company to close  the transaction.
